      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E_rms) for NIH predictions must be < 8% with uncertainty bounds reported.",
      "rationale": "E_rms for NIH is 9.3% across the five operating points, exceeding the 8% criterion. Uncertainty bounds are reported via Monte Carlo. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
